latestPosts.caption:
Why Did Swiggy Launch Instamart?

Every month we host an industry leader at Honasa for a session of 'Honest Chats' with our CEO Varun Alagh. 

Watch Swiggy's co-founder Phani Kishan Addepalli share the process behind Swiggy's venture into quick commerce. He explained how the company recognized a rising demand for fast, convenient grocery shopping and how Instamart was created to meet that need. In part one of the conversation, Addepalli delves into the strategic thinking behind entering a new market segment and expanding Swiggy's reach beyond its food delivery roots.

Here’s to our winners who inspired us the most this month!

latestPosts.caption:
This quarter has been a valuable learning experience. Just like the slingshot effect, we have taken a step back in order to build a stronger momentum for our future breakthroughs. 

Our market landscape is evolving with new consumer demand trends, digital media driving decision-making, and quick commerce making purchasing easier than ever. We are refining our playbook, laying strong foundational steps, and focusing on a sustained growth path. 

Our vision is to shape the future of India’s beauty and personal care sector remains unwavering, and we are committed to innovation, disruption, and excellence through dedicated R&D. 

Here’s to building a future rooted in resilience and forward-thinking together. Thank you for your trust and support.

latestPosts.caption:
As we celebrate India’s 78th Independence Day, it’s a moment to reflect on our journey as a nation and the strides we’ve made in building a self-reliant India.

At Honasa Consumer Ltd., our mission is deeply rooted in this very ethos.

From the inception, we have always strived to create products that resonate with the values, traditions, and needs of every Indian household.

Each product we innovate is a testament to our commitment to quality, sustainability, and the belief that the best solutions come from within our own country. We are proud to contribute to the ‘Aatmanirbhar Bharat’ vision, empowering local communities and creating a positive impact in every step of our journey.

Today, let’s celebrate the spirit of independence by embracing and supporting brands that are truly ‘Made in India, for Indians.’

Happy Independence Day to all!

#HappyIndependenceDay2024 #Honasa #India

Honasa Consumer is proud to announce its expansion to more than 1,000 Smart Bazaar and Smart Point Reliance Retail stores across India. 🚀

This strategic move enhances the availability of @mamaearth.in , making high-quality products more accessible to consumers nationwide.

By partnering with Reliance Retail, we aim to boost market presence, increase brand visibility, and serve many new customers. This expansion aligns with our commitment to quality, innovation, and sustainability.

At Honasa, we look forward to continued growth and delivering exceptional value to our customers through this significant milestone.
